### TKT-008 — Ping returning no results on Linux

**Symptom:** Ping requests return empty or malformed results after migrating the app from macOS to the Ubuntu VM.

**Cause:** The regex patterns in `api/ping.py` were written against macOS ping output format. Linux ping uses different output strings:

| Field | macOS format | Linux format |
|---|---|---|
| Packets received | `packets received` | `received` |
| Round-trip stats | `min/avg/max/stddev` | `rtt min/avg/max/mdev` |

**Resolution:** Updated regex patterns in `api/ping.py` to match Linux ping output format. Both strings differ enough that macOS patterns silently fail to match on Linux, returning empty results rather than an error.
